
Ranger Help for: weapons
========================

SUMMARY:    
Rangers are proficient in medium sized swords and daggers. As well as 
some larger blunt polearms, such as staves. Rangers can double wield
most of these weapons, except for the larger ones. The defining weapon
for a Ranger is his or her bow. Ranger carved bows aren't set as missile
type weapons, so a Ranger doesn't have to be specialized in missile weapons
to use them, they are medium blunt weapons, since that is how a Ranger
uses it in hand to hand combat. There main advantage is the volleys of
arrows you can shoot at your opponents.

